<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Office for Zero Emission Vehicles (OZEV) is a team working across government to support the transition to zero emission vehicles (ZEVs). We are providing support for the take-up of plug in vehicles, as well as funding to support chargepoint infrastructure across the UK. This will contribute to economic growth and will help reduce greenhouse gas emissions and air pollution on our roads."@en .
